Losing you // with @haleykrolack // Swipe to see the full set üíô‚Å†‚†Ä
‚Å†‚†Ä
I think many of us are dealing with emotionally challenging situations at the moment... it feels like many of us are drifting, whether due to concrete issues and difficult situations, or just due to the current instability of the world. ‚Å†‚†Ä
I'm finding myself in a bit of a rough patch as of the last few weeks, so it feels like a bit of a remedy to share this set right now. It reminds me that, as long as I keep moving, I will find a way to pass through the situation. ‚Å†‚†Ä
‚Å†‚†Ä
To me, this set feels like a progression of letting something go.  Haley is looking out, trying to hold on to something that is long gone... but then she ultimately manages to accept that it is lost, and comforts herself in parting ways with it. ‚Å†‚†Ä
‚†Ä
A huge thank you to Haley for doing such INCREDIBLE work despite it being very unpleasantly cold and rainy! & a major thank you to @stillsincolor for heading out there with us üôè Appreciate you two immensely! ‚†Ä
